        <div class = 'container'>
            <div class = 'row'>
                <div class = 'col-6-md' id = 'D2velocityGraph'></div>
                <div class = 'col-6-md'>
                    <ol type = 'a'>
                        <li>Determine the displacement of the object from 0 to 4 s. </li>
                        <li>Determine the displacement of the object from 4 s to 10 s.</li>
